- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant because the paper presents two encodings of DES as logic programs and discusses their computational properties. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is possible because the paper discusses the representation of DES using normal logic programs. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also possible because the paper evaluates the performance of the encodings and Smodels system in solving the DES problem.
